{"type": "article", "id": 23867, "title": "黄色沙袋沙发", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-15T07:00:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607165701Jv7u9UC3l8Ehc4DK.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这把带脚蹬的沙发是由丹麦设计师 Ineke Hans 为比利时设计品牌 Moome 设计的。它的外形非常方正，厚实的软垫让沙发看上去像一个沙袋。金属结构和沙发本身都是统一的黄色，连成一个整体，让沙袋的气体看起来更大，也使人感受到轻松。当初设计时只想做一个放垫子的结构，而名字“plof”的意思是重重地落下。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607165659HXiFwgVL3Ayk7cex.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.88675214\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607165659S7prnUvVX2ulmyzJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66773504\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607165700OxLEqwN1MFSKpm4I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607165700ZBdqIH4TQxXeylgC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66773504\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}